{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Life jackets must be worn if in sea on inflatable, boat, kayak etc",
        "additional_details": "You get fines for not wearing a seat belt? What\u2019s the difference?\r\n \r\nMy two children lost their father two weeks ago when he went into the sea on his kayak without a life jacket, lifeguards and search teams searched hours for two days until he sadly washed up dead two days later. Me and my children are heartbroken. And the family also. I would like water safety to be taught better in the UK to make sure these stricter rules are followed. ",
        "background": "On the spot fine \u00a3200 for anyone who is seen not wearing a life jacket. Patrol lifeguards should have the power to monitor beaches and require anyone found without one to be called out the sea and fined.",
